{
  "texts": [
    "Fit-RAG [18] introduces a method that uses detailed prompts to ensure deep question understanding and clear reasoning in fact retrieval.",
    "Domain-specific knowledge graphs [19]- [22] have been effectively employed in KG-based RAG systems within LLMs [23]- [25] for question-answering tasks [26], [27].",
    "While most efforts focus on enhancing LLMs by augmenting knowledge graphs with relevant facts, there has been limited work on improving the reasoning capabilities of LLMs during knowledge retrieval.",
    "Our research with Mindful-RAG aims to establish a road map for advancing these methods by leveraging the model's inherent knowledge for better question understanding.",
    "We conducted an error analysis of KG-based RAG methods integrated with LLMs for question-answering tasks, identifying eight critical failure points, categorized into reasoning failures and structural limitations."
  ]
}